        "created_at": "2020-08-29T23:55:35.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=2817875&amp;iNote=8602405\"><strong>2016 Domaine Pattes Loup Chablis Vent d\u2019Ange</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, Chablis (8/29/2020)</em><br>\nCrystalline purity, with a bit of extra weight from the vintage. It still has a bright acid core to frame the lemon and stone flavors, with a touch of nut skin bitterness on the finish. It\u2019s not so much a laser, but more a focused beam that covers the entire palate. Wholly satisfying.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
