        "created_at": "2020-08-31T13:13:13.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019ve been a fan of Pattes Loup for several years\u2026it\u2019s the \u201cpurity\u201d.  Increasingly scarce and expensive\u2026not helped by the tariff and Euro valuations.  I\u2019m down to a handful of Chablis in the cellar which is sad and slightly depressing.  Thankfully, Oregon is scratching my Chard itch these days, but there can be no real replacement.</p>\n<p>RT</p>",
